---
title: Mushroom & Blackbean Wellington with Thyme-Roasted Carrots
description: Comfort food at its finest, our show-stopping wellington is made with juicy mushrooms and blackbeans for a delicious veggie twist. Served with thyme-roasted carrots that are roasted until sweet and tender and golden, crispy potatoes, this is a recipe worth staying in for.
